&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d20166.245533131485!2d127.05221952465662!3d37.24807568684908!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x357b44eada4c9a3b%3A0x8ab0c82b89d2e0b5!2z6rmM6rys672A6rys!5e0!3m2!1sko!2skr!4v1775639238430!5m2!1sko!2skr" width="600" height="450" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
&lt;p&gt;가죽공방 다녀오는 길에 문득 간판이 보였다. &lt;strong&gt;&amp;ldquo;히피펌 전문&amp;rdquo;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;기분전환 겸 머리에 뭔짓을 할까 고민하던 차에, 잘됬다 싶어 오늘 아침에 전화해서 예약 잡고, 청소하고 씻고 바로 다녀옴.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;결론부터 말하자면&amp;hellip;.굳! 며칠 지나봐야 알겠지만, 잘 안풀리게 오래가게 강하게 해달라고 요청드렸으니&amp;hellip;.오래 가겠지?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;가격은 7.5만원&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class="gallery-image" data-flex-basis="180px" data-flex-grow="75" height="4032" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px" src="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040803/1.jpg" srcset="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040803/1_hu_74e4db05858dc9bd.jpg 800w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040803/1_hu_692635232301112f.jpg 1600w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040803/1_hu_992fe47f09f14bcc.jpg 2400w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040803/1.jpg 3024w" width="3024"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;너무 못생겨서 얼굴은 좀 가리자&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class="gallery-image" data-flex-basis="180px" data-flex-grow="75" height="4032" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px" src="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040803/2.jpg" srcset="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040803/2_hu_bc294e1b1b917985.jpg 800w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040803/2_hu_ba2d3ebb9d1595a7.jpg 1600w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040803/2_hu_1ddd1e8cd67e9438.jpg 2400w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040803/2.jpg 3024w" width="3024"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;이쯤해서 원장님이 커피를 권하심.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;안마신다고 했더니 요구르트를 주셨다&amp;hellip;.ㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋ 감사해라. 그러고나서 컵라면도 권하심&amp;hellip;서비스는 감사하나 굳이 점심으로 컵라면을 먹고싶지는 않아서 정중히 사양..&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class="gallery-image" data-flex-basis="180px" data-flex-grow="75" height="4032" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px" src="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040803/4.jpg" srcset="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040803/4_hu_c15998d205053749.jpg 800w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040803/4_hu_b87116f0e7783e89.jpg 1600w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040803/4_hu_93abcd12abee4c93.jpg 2400w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040803/4.jpg 3024w" width="3024"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;투블럭을 권하셨으나, 어무이가 투블럭을 별로 안좋아하시기에 그냥 구렛나루는 다듬어달라고 했음.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class="gallery-image" data-flex-basis="180px" data-flex-grow="75" height="3088" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px" src="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040803/5.jpg" srcset="https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040803/5_hu_a03d99d68e3f0b13.jpg 800w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040803/5_hu_dff5cad154aade3.jpg 1600w, https://dongheon-dev.github.io/reviewlog/post/26040803/5.jpg 2316w" width="2316"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
